<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l26"><expan>beſcheide<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeit / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ew die ſache <expan>fleiſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> laſſet <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l27">ſein durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ıca<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
