<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
                        etc. ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>, wie daz man von
                                <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> spitals
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ein <expan>küntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vor
                        ew czu <expan>Sib<ex>er</ex>g</expan> auf den
                        <app><note><q type="date"><expan>nehstkunff<ex>tigen</ex></expan> suntag</q>06.04.1410</note></app>
<expan>süch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müsz von eins guts
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> czu <expan>Wenge<ex>n</ex></expan>, das
                        hinter <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> spital ligt, darczu ir czu einem
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hörer</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>bescheide<ex>n</ex></expan> seit.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ew die sache
                                <expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> lasset
                            <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica<ex>m</ex></expan> quasimodo
                            <expan>ge<ex>n</ex>iti</expan>
<expan>a<ex>nno</ex></expan> x<hi rend="sup">mo</hi>. </ab>
</div>
